{"tid":845653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"財困耶教組織「影音使團」今個星期六(10月6日)全港賣旗","createTime":"2018-10-02T23:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T03:40:47.000Z","uid":136994,"like":2,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"04173c88eb8f9d8007bb0101d41b548f9c0b28e5","tid":845653,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:58:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.media.org.hk/tme_main/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.media.org.hk%2Ftme_main%2F&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f6ff677a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.media.org.hk/tme_main/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/075317_16b831e332fb9a33d0aae6ae83908199.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F075317_16b831e332fb9a33d0aae6ae83908199.png&h=a3230df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/storage/asset/section/1576/tc/FD_list_18-19_20180810.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Fstorage%2Fasset%2Fsection%2F1576%2Ftc%2FFD_list_18-19_20180810.pdf&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=21486723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/storage/asset/section/1576/tc/FD_list_18-19_20180810.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/075323_656486fa75d1274673a3cc9822923554.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F075323_656486fa75d1274673a3cc9822923554.png&h=ff1cd4ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc3ba0d3e770fa41af182667321d3ba3ae07e522","tid":845653,"uid":136994,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:58:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://apostlesmedia.com/20180804/8739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2F20180804%2F8739&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=8b41b46f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://apostlesmedia.com/20180804/8739</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《影音財困》影音使團不務正業賣月餅</span><br />\nBy 門徒媒體 - 2018-08-0401984<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://apostlesmedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/螢幕快照-2018-08-03-19.09.41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-08-03-19.09.41.png&h=53b18d61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影音使團早前於Youtube發佈籌募短片，指機構急需資金。那邊廂，旗下的天使心月刊則不務正務，自製月餅。財困一說，只是為了不惜欠債失見證地傳福音，暫時未知員工是否有欠薪的情況出現。<br />\n<br />\n影音使團早前在在其網頁及代禱家書上作出緊急呼籲，指機構巳經沒有流動資金，急需募得780萬元渡過難關。有資深會計師表示，創世電視好大喜功，租下天價製作中心，又要維持100名同工，理財不善，自製財困。今日記者發現影音使團在Youtube的籌募短片已被移除，未知其原因。<br />\n<br />\n影音使團旗下《天使心月刊》，利用中秋節賣月餅。宣傳海報中稱「將屬天的祝福帶給鄰舍，使更多未信的朋友能夠在這佳節認識上帝，與祂團圓」，意指送月餅之人希望鄰舍能（死後）見上帝，宣傳資料曝光後，在網上被信徒恥笑「不務正業」。"},{"pid":"aa27279fdd630e50039ba65b07f606499ca6c912","tid":845653,"uid":136994,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:00:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://apostlesmedia.com/20180731/8698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2F20180731%2F8698&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3aeeb881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://apostlesmedia.com/20180731/8698</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">影音使團陷財困　急籌780萬救亡創世電視</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nBy 門徒媒體 - 2018-07-31024478<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://apostlesmedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/image1-2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fimage1-2.jpeg&h=32286b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影音使團繼上年11月急籌千萬後，不足一年，又宣佈財困、欠租、拖欠薪金，急需780萬應付短期現金需要。<br />\n<br />\n影音使團在網頁及代禱家書上作出緊急呼籲，創世電視總監葉家寶表示，機構巳經沒有流動資金，急需募得780萬元渡過難關，包括100名同工薪酬210萬、鴻圖道1號三個月租金，合共320萬，以及半年平台租賃費250萬，他希望支持者可以幫助解決經濟危機。為了應付天價租金，機構推出 《創世百人》認獻行動，目標一百人參與，每人每月認獻1萬去支持租金。<br />\n<br />\n《門徒媒體》記者發現，影音使團鮮有在製作中心製作節目，不明白為何要以天價，在市區租製作中心。自從使團租了鴻圖道1號作廣播製作中心，頻頻出現財困。根據該機構最後公佈的2015年感恩年報 (非法定賬目)顯示，當年已經是流動負債 (流動資金少於流動債務)。在財政不健康的環境下，居然以天價過百萬，月租製作中心，又要支持過百名員工薪酬，恐怕創世電視總監葉家寶未能從亞洲電視失敗吸取教訓，又要不停 「撲水」。"},{"pid":"f50b673bbc2eb1014c22ed6fc7c3a398e6b2f68f","tid":845653,"uid":141151,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:03:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">為了應付天價租金，機構推出 《創世百人》認獻行動，目標一百人參與，每人每月認獻1萬去支持租金。<br />\n<br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10405344d7796f9862b72e9bc09351eb0976f56e","tid":845653,"uid":136994,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:12:58.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n上次有巴打唔知道工賊會賣旗結果中伏<br />\n今次就早啲提醒等大家唔好再犯同樣嘅錯"},{"pid":"22916b69998a3740c0e162cb048f9478d46fd14a","tid":845653,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:14:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"943bcde3a28e48a0f6981a97b082ddc73fe9dbf0","tid":845653,"uid":84275,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:15:21.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話係搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣尺數係屯門廠廈租已經平一半<br />\n搞電視台呢壇野由day1開始就預左係蝕住做，無廣告仲要買電視台時段，你唔係以為自己收入會多過亞視下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預左蝕做仲要豪洗，明顯係預左兄弟姊妹們個個月要科水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0100b0214fce3d8966c9a5acbd0ee3b322d7a736","tid":845653,"uid":8048,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:15:29.000Z","msg":"財困係神嘅考驗嚟"},{"pid":"88c2d0e05f70a01756e7a12bb25d7da8dc470166","tid":845653,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:15:47.00