ke":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:27:45.000Z","msg":"到底係葉家寶自己有問題做親都咁黑仔<br />\n定係佢自己就係專幫人執笠救火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3af25b2c83a80b522e1bc17d2c60f28fdb8d6d1","tid":845653,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:29:36.000Z","msg":"財困邪教組織影陰屎團<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba536042f203fbeb02805e1cf7759c0bb610513","tid":845653,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc3ba0d3e770fa41af182667321d3ba3ae07e522","tid":845653,"uid":136994,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:58:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://apostlesmedia.com/20180804/8739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2F20180804%2F8739&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=8b41b46f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://apostlesmedia.com/20180804/8739</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《影音財困》影音使團不務正業賣月餅</span><br />\nBy 門徒媒體 - 2018-08-0401984<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://apostlesmedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/螢幕快照-2018-08-03-19.09.41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-08-03-19.09.41.png&h=53b18d61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影音使團早前於Youtube發佈籌募短片，指機構急需資金。那邊廂，旗下的天使心月刊則不務正務，自製月餅。財困一說，只是為了不惜欠債失見證地傳福音，暫時未知員工是否有欠薪的情況出現。<br />\n<br />\n影音使團早前在在其網頁及代禱家書上作出緊急呼籲，指機構巳經沒有流動資金，急需募得780萬元渡過難關。有資深會計師表示，創世電視好大喜功，租下天價製作中心，又要維持100名同工，理財不善，自製財困。今日記者發現影音使團在Youtube的籌募短片已被移除，未知其原因。<br />\n<br />\n影音使團旗下《天使心月刊》，利用中秋節賣月餅。宣傳海報中稱「將屬天的祝福帶給鄰舍，使更多未信的朋友能夠在這佳節認識上帝，與祂團圓」，意指送月餅之人希望鄰舍能（死後）見上帝，宣傳資料曝光後，在網上被信徒恥笑「不務正業」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:30:28.000Z","msg":"我睇到香港高鐵嘅未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2a594e81d8d972704071a5ede03eb585089fef","tid":845653,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"943bcde3a28e48a0f6981a97b082ddc73fe9dbf0","tid":845653,"uid":84275,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:15:21.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話係搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣尺數係屯門廠廈租已經平一半<br />\n搞電視台呢壇野由day1開始就預左係蝕住做，無廣告仲要買電視台時段，你唔係以為自己收入會多過亞視下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預左蝕做仲要豪洗，明顯係預左兄弟姊妹們個個月要科水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"好似租左牛頭角嗰邊，唔知而家仲係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50ff9b849d969c66ddf4a0a3fa4505800c5d49b","tid":845653,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3a26c17e24de30547dc6cfc7f72919ac22fa721","tid":845653,"uid":53805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:17:19.000Z","msg":"早十年搵到方舟架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"畀山竹吹走左喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ddec096310f145cd7b1a3e87170f712a543c93","tid":845653,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"937c6cbdb5fc68fd05fc5c0820cac0d9d375abcb","tid":845653,"uid":84619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:53:08.000Z","msg":"係神比你既考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:32:28.000Z","msg":"財困係神嘅安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\